00:11:57,560 --> 00:12:00,360
<font color="yellow">...sudah tahu kalau Dae Mok mendudukkan si palsu ke takhta,
namun...</font>

189
00:12:00,820 --> 00:12:02,160
<font color="yellow">...untuk mengatakan yang sebenarnya,</font>

190
00:12:04,090 --> 00:12:05,090
<font color="yellow">aku khawatir...</font>

191
00:12:05,890 --> 00:12:08,260
<font color="yellow">...istana akan bersimbah darah lagi,</font>

192
00:12:09,360 --> 00:12:10,360
<font color="yellow">sehingga...</font>

193
00:12:10,990 --> 00:12:13,290
<font color="yellow">...memilih untuk menutup mulut.</font>

194
00:12:14,790 --> 00:12:17,760
<font color="yellow">Semua ini, kesalahanku.</font>

195
00:12:20,760 --> 00:12:22,720
<font color="yellow">Dengarkan aku, kalian semua!</font>

196
00:12:25,320 --> 00:12:26,390
<font color="yellow">Dia...</font>

197
00:12:27,320 --> 00:12:28,390
<font color="yellow">...adalah...</font>

198
00:12:29,660 --> 00:12:31,020
<font color="yellow">..Seja asli.</font>

199
00:12:43,890 --> 00:12:45,660
<font color="yellow">Bagaimana Anda bisa seyakin itu?</font>

200
00:12:45,760 --> 00:12:49,890
<font color="yellow">Anda juga tidak pernah melihat wajah Seja Jeoha sebelumnya.</font>

201
00:12:50,120 --> 00:12:51,160
<font color="yellow">Aku ini...</font>

202
00:12:51,890 --> 00:12:53,590
<font color="yellow">...ibunya Seja.</font>

203
00:12:54,990 --> 00:12:56,460
<font color="yellow">Bagaimana bisa seorang Ibu...</font>

204
00:12:57,260 --> 00:12:59,220
<font color="yellow">...tidak mengenali anaknya sendiri?
(So touching...)</font>

205
00:13:02,120 --> 00:13:05,720
<font color="yellow">Ada satu lagi bukti bahwa pria itu adalah Seja Jeoha yang asli.</font>

206
00:13:16,360 --> 00:13:18,220
<font color="yellow">Seja Jeoha yang asli...</font>

207
00:13:19,120 --> 00:13:20,390
<font color="yellow">...akan mengalami...</font>

208
00:13:21,260 --> 00:13:23,020
<font color="yellow">...proses penyembuhan sendiri saat teracuni.</font>

209
00:13:24,390 --> 00:13:25,860
<font color="yellow">Proses penyembuhan sendiri?</font>

210
00:13:25,860 --> 00:13:27,620
<font color="yellow">Seja Jeoha yang asli,</font>

211
00:13:27,620 --> 00:13:30,860
<font color="yellow">memiliki darah istimewa yang membuatnya dapat sembuh
dengan sendirinya apabila terkena racun.</font>

212
00:13:31,860 --> 00:13:33,190
<font color="yellow">Pada hari dia lahir ke dunia,</font>

213
00:13:35,090 --> 00:13:36,460
<font color="yellow">ada seseorang yang telah...</font>

214
00:13:36,460 --> 00:13:39,890
<font color="yellow">...meracuninya, hingga kemudian ia memiliki imunitas tersebut.</font>

215
00:13:39,890 --> 00:13:40,890
<font color="yellow">Racun apa?</font>

216
00:13:41,320 --> 00:13:42,960
<font color="yellow">Saya belum pernah dengar itu sebelumnya.</font>

217
00:13:42,960 --> 00:13:45,890
<font color="yellow">Seja Jeoha mengidap penyakit serius ditandai demam tinggi--</font>

218
00:13:45,890 --> 00:13:46,890
<font color="yellow">Semua orang...</font>

219
00:13:47,220 --> 00:13:49,660
<font color="yellow">...memercayai Jeoha saat itu terkena demam tinggi,</font>

220
00:13:49,990 --> 00:13:51,020
<font color="yellow">namun,</font>

221
00:13:53,020 --> 00:13:54,590
<font color="yellow">sebenarnya ia diracuni.</font>

222
00:13:55,520 --> 00:13:56,860
<font color="yellow">Malam itu, aku...</font>

223
00:13:56,890 --> 00:13:58,960
<font color="yellow">...berada bersamanya.</font>

224
00:13:58,960 --> 00:14:00,760
<font color="yellow">Hentikan kebohonganmu itu!</font>

225
00:14:00,990 --> 00:14:04,020
<font color="yellow">Bukankah akibat ketidakbecusanmu merawat Jeoha saat baru lahir...</font>

226
00:14:04,660 --> 00:14:06,960
<font color="yellow">...kau dipecat dari posisimu saat itu?</font>

227
00:14:06,960 --> 00:14:10,190
<font color="yellow">Kau dan Tabib Kerajaan kala itu dipecat bersama.</font>

228
00:14:10,520 --> 00:14:12,320
<font color="yellow">- Itu!
- Seja...</font>

229
00:14:16,790 --> 00:14:18,990
<font color="yellow">Benar bahwa ia telah diracuni.</font>

230
00:14:22,460 --> 00:14:25,260
<font color="yellow">Lalu, yang meracuni Jeoha kala itu,</font>

231
00:14:25,260 --> 00:14:26,890
<font color="yellow">siapa yang memiliki nyali besar begitu?</font>

232
00:14:26,990 --> 00:14:28,120
<font color="yellow">Itu...</font>

233
00:14:31,320 --> 00:14:32,890
<font color="yellow">Itu... sebenarnya...</font>

234
00:14:36,060 --> 00:14:37,490
<font color="yellow">Aku orangnya.</font>

235
00:14:39,390 --> 00:14:42,190
<font color="yellow">Aku memihak Dae Mook kala itu.</font>

236
00:14:44,190 --> 00:14:45,260
<font color="yellow">Sebab itu, aku...</font>

237
00:14:46,360 --> 00:14:48,190
<font color="yellow">...mencoba meracuninya.</font>

238
00:14:52,060 --> 00:14:53,660
<font color="yellow">Bagaimana bisa kami memercayainya?</font>

239
00:14:53,820 --> 00:14:56,320
<font color="yellow">Karena Anda disingkirkan dari kediaman Ibu Suri,</font>

240
00:14:56,320 --> 00:14:58,990
<font color="yellow">Anda mencoba melimpahkan semua kesalahan pada Dae Mok Eureushin.</font>

241
00:16:14,890 --> 00:16:17,990
<font color="yellow">[Tabung Plasenta Selir Young Bin]</font>

242
00:16:29,820 --> 00:16:31,260
<font color="yellow">- Siapa di sana?
- Diam!</font>

243
00:16:40,360 --> 00:16:42,160
<font color="yellow">- Sudah ketemu?
- Ya.</font>

244
00:16:42,220 --> 00:16:43,820
<font color="yellow">Sekarang juga, lekas ke Geunjeongjeon.</font>

245
00:16:43,820 --> 00:16:46,020
<font color="yellow">Tolong berikan tabung plasenta itu pada Ibu Suri.</font>

246
00:16:46,190 --> 00:16:48,320
<font color="yellow">Beliau akan mengonfirmasi identitas Seja Jeoha.</font>

247
00:16:48,560 --> 00:16:50,420
<font color="yellow">- Ya.
- Di sana.</font>

248
00:16:50,520 --> 00:16:52,320
<font color="yellow">- Tangkap dia!
- Sekarang!</font>

249
00:16:54,820 --> 00:16:57,890
<font color="yellow">Seja Jeoha telah diracuni, apa Anda punya buktinya?</font>

250
00:16:57,890 --> 00:16:59,160
<font color="yellow">Ada buktinya.</font>

251
00:16:59,520 --> 00:17:00,660
<font color="yellow">Beliau kebal.</font>

252
00:17:00,860 --> 00:17:03,720
<font color="yellow">Kekebalan beliau terhadap racun membuktikannya!</font>

253
00:17:03,890 --> 00:17:06,060
<font color="yellow">Saat Seja Jeoha asli...</font>

254
00:17:07,390 --> 00:17:10,420
<font color="yellow">...diracuni, di bahu kirinya...</font>

255
00:17:10,660 --> 00:17:13,160
<font color="yellow">...karakter "Sun" akan muncul.</font>

256
00:17:13,830 --> 00:17:17,260
<font color="yellow">Tidak ada kisah semacam itu yang tercatat.</font>

257
00:17:17,260 --> 00:17:20,790
<font color="yellow">Itu benar!
Bagaimana kau akan membuktikan bahwa ucapanmu itu...</font>

258
00:17:20,790 --> 00:17:22,220
<font color="yellow">...bukanlah kebohongan?</font>

259
00:17:35,860 --> 00:17:36,960
<font color="yellow">Siapa?</font>

260
00:17:40,420 --> 00:17:43,420
<font color="yellow">Geunjeongjeon dilarang dimasuki oleh siapa pun, itu titah Raja.</font>

261
00:17:43,520 --> 00:17:44,890
<font color="yellow">Kau harus pergi!</font>

262
00:17:53,490 --> 00:17:56,090
<font color="yellow">Aghassi, Anda sudah siap?</font>

263
00:18:16,420 --> 00:18:19,420
<font color="yellow">Buktikan pada kami sekarang juga bahwa dia kebal terhadap racun!</font>

264
00:18:19,520 --> 00:18:21,660
<font color="yellow">Pasti itu hanyalah bualan belaka...</font>

265
00:18:21,660 --> 00:18:23,290
<font color="yellow">...karena dia tidak bisa membuktikannya.</font>

266
00:18:33,020 --> 00:18:34,160
<font color="yellow">Daebi Mama.</font>

267
00:18:34,590 --> 00:18:38,060
<font color="yellow">Siapa Jusang Cheonha yang asli, saya membawa bukti
yang dapat memverifikasinya.</font>

268
00:18:38,220 --> 00:18:39,390
<font color="yellow">Daebi Mama.</font>

269
00:18:39,720 --> 00:18:42,590
<font color="yellow">Saya membawa buktinya, jadi tolong buka pintunya.</font>

270
00:18:42,590 --> 00:18:45,420
<font color="yellow">- Apa yang terjadi?
- Buka pintunya!</font>

271
00:18:57,960 --> 00:19:00,120
<font color="yellow">- Kau itu siapa?
- Saya...</font>

272
00:19:00,990 --> 00:19:02,520
<font color="yellow">...adalah putri...</font>

273
00:19:03,120 --> 00:19:05,690
<font color="yellow">...mendiang Hakim Hanseongbu, Han Gyu Ho.</font>

274
00:19:06,360 --> 00:19:07,590
<font color="yellow">Saya Han Ga Eun.</font>

275
00:19:08,090 --> 00:19:09,890
<font color="yellow">Di malam mendiang Raja dibunuh,</font>

276
00:19:10,060 --> 00:19:13,520
<font color="yellow">saya sedang bersama Selir Young Bin.</font>

277
00:19:15,330 --> 00:19:17,790
<font color="yellow">Tepat sebelum Selir Young Bin menghembuskan napas terakhir,</font>

278
00:19:18,260 --> 00:19:22,020
<font color="yellow">beliau mengatakan kepada saya perihal tabung plasenta ini.</font>

279
00:19:26,330 --> 00:19:29,890
<font color="yellow">Ini adalah tabung plasenta dari Seja Jeoha.</font>

280
00:19:30,060 --> 00:19:32,960
<font color="yellow">Di dalamnya, terdapat bukti Seja Jeoha yang asli.</font>

281
00:19:33,420 --> 00:19:34,790
<font color="yellow">Mohon diperiksa.</font>

282
00:19:35,290 --> 00:19:36,860
<font color="yellow">Kau mendekatlah ke sini.</font>

283
00:20:24,220 --> 00:20:28,160
<font color="yellow">Ini adalah surat tulisan tangan mendiang Raja.</font>

284
00:20:28,420 --> 00:20:29,620
<font color="yellow">Juga...</font>

285
00:20:30,720 --> 00:20:32,620
<font color="yellow">...memiliki stempel Raja.</font>

286
00:20:35,060 --> 00:20:36,490
<font color="yellow">Siapa saja yang curiga,</font>

287
00:20:36,560 --> 00:20:39,660
<font color="yellow">mendekatlah dan periksa sendiri surat ini.</font>

288
00:20:46,290 --> 00:20:47,760
<font color="yellow">Bila Seja asli...</font>

289
00:20:48,360 --> 00:20:51,520
<font color="yellow">...secara sengaja maupun tidak terkena racun,</font>

290
00:20:52,160 --> 00:20:56,520
<font color="yellow">di bahu kirinya, akan muncul karakter "Sun".</font>

291
00:21:00,890 --> 00:21:03,620
<font color="yellow">Cangkir ini berisi racun.</font>

292
00:21:04,060 --> 00:21:05,830
<font color="yellow">Seja yang asli...</font>

293
00:21:05,960 --> 00:21:07,190
<font color="yellow">...akan imun...</font>

294
00:21:07,190 --> 00:21:10,020
<font color="yellow">...dan tetap selamat meski meminumnya.</font>

295
00:21:11,490 --> 00:21:13,060
<font color="yellow">Siapa pun di antara keduanya yang selamat,</font>

296
00:21:13,190 --> 00:21:15,790
<font color="yellow">maka dialah Seja yang asli.</font>

297
00:21:15,860 --> 00:21:19,520
<font color="yellow">Berarti juga, ia adalah Raja yang asli dari Joseon.</font>

298
00:21:25,760 --> 00:21:27,560
<font color="yellow">Jika kau yang asli,</font>

299
00:21:28,830 --> 00:21:30,830
<font color="yellow">buktikan dengan meminum ini.</font>

300
00:21:35,120 --> 00:21:37,120
<font color="yellow">Kenapa kau tidak meminumnya?</font>

301
00:21:38,890 --> 00:21:40,760
<font color="yellow">Bila kau memang Seja asli,</font>

302
00:21:40,960 --> 00:21:43,860
<font color="yellow">minumlah racun ini sekarang juga.</font>

303
00:21:44,460 --> 00:21:48,120
<font color="yellow">Buktikan kepada dunia bahwa kau adalah Raja yang asli.</font>

304
00:22:00,690 --> 00:22:01,890
<font color="yellow">Jangan, Sun-ah.</font>

305
00:22:05,660 --> 00:22:07,460
<font color="yellow">Jangan meminumnya, kumohon.</font>

306
00:22:38,860 --> 00:22:40,690
<font color="yellow">Dia meminumnya!</font>

307
00:22:40,790 --> 00:22:42,420
<font color="yellow">Dia bisa mati.</font>

308
00:22:51,460 --> 00:22:52,490
<font color="yellow">Jeoha.</font>

309
00:23:12,790 --> 00:23:13,860
<font color="yellow">Seja, kau,</font>

310
00:23:14,860 --> 00:23:19,020
<font color="yellow">tunjukkan bahu kirimu kepada kami semua.</font>

311
00:23:54,820 --> 00:23:57,560
<font color="yellow">Kau mungkin bisa menipu dunia untuk sementara, Lee Sun-ah.</font>

312
00:23:58,760 --> 00:24:00,060
<font color="yellow">Namun dusta...</font>

313
00:24:00,890 --> 00:24:03,260
<font color="yellow">...tidak akan pernah mengalahkan kebenaran.</font>

314
00:24:06,090 --> 00:24:09,120
<font color="yellow">Sekarang, kebenaran sudah terungkap.</font>

315
00:24:09,120 --> 00:24:10,490
<font color="yellow">Tunggu apa lagi?</font>

316
00:24:10,890 --> 00:24:13,460
<font color="yellow">- Tahan si palsu ini!
- Baik.</font>

317
00:24:38,590 --> 00:24:39,790
<font color="yellow">Dia...</font>

318
00:24:41,320 --> 00:24:43,560
<font color="yellow">...sekalipun dia Seja asli,</font>

319
00:24:45,060 --> 00:24:46,720
<font color="yellow">memang apa perbedaannya?</font>

320
00:24:47,160 --> 00:24:48,320
<font color="yellow">Lee Sun-ah.</font>

321
00:24:49,020 --> 00:24:50,660
<font color="yellow">Hentikan sekarang juga.</font>

322
00:24:50,720 --> 00:24:51,990
<font color="yellow">Kalian semua!!!</font>

323
00:24:53,690 --> 00:24:55,290
<font color="yellow">Sampai hari ini kalian membungkuk padaku...</font>

324
00:24:56,160 --> 00:24:58,690
<font color="yellow">...meski sudah mengetahui kebenarannya,
apa itu salah?</font>

325
00:25:00,620 --> 00:25:01,890
<font color="yellow">Sejak awal,</font>

326
00:25:04,120 --> 00:25:06,690
<font color="yellow">Anda juga mengetahui kebenarannya.</font>

327
00:25:07,620 --> 00:25:08,760
<font color="yellow">Baiklah.</font>

328
00:25:10,620 --> 00:25:12,490
<font color="yellow">Pria itu, kita anggap benar bahwa dia...</font>

329
00:25:13,390 --> 00:25:15,520
<font color="yellow">...putra mendiang Raja, pewaris takhta yang sah.</font>

330
00:25:15,860 --> 00:25:17,990
<font color="yellow">Namun, apakah kebenaran itu...</font>

331
00:25:18,290 --> 00:25:21,020
<font color="yellow">...lebih berharga dibanding nyawa kalian semua?</font>

332
00:25:21,020 --> 00:25:22,060
<font color="yellow">Dia benar!</font>

333
00:25:22,060 --> 00:25:25,720
<font color="yellow">Siapa pun yang dipilih Dae Mok Eureushin, itulah Raja yang asli.</font>

334
00:25:26,320 --> 00:25:29,460
<font color="yellow">Kalian pikir, siapa yang memegang kendali atas nyawa kalian?</font>

335
00:25:30,420 --> 00:25:32,260
<font color="yellow">Kalian semua, pikirkan itu baik-baik!</font>

336
00:25:33,590 --> 00:25:35,190
<font color="yellow">Perdana Menteri benar.</font>

337
00:25:36,890 --> 00:25:41,260
<font color="yellow">Di dunia ini, tidak ada yang lebih penting daripada nyawa kita.</font>

338
00:25:42,760 --> 00:25:44,620
<font color="yellow">Kalian semua bukanlah pecundang...</font>

339
00:25:45,390 --> 00:25:47,290
<font color="yellow">...ataupun pengecut.</font>

340
00:25:47,460 --> 00:25:48,620
<font color="yellow">Namun, sekarang...</font>

341
00:25:51,020 --> 00:25:52,120
<font color="yellow">...kalian semua...</font>

342
00:25:53,090 --> 00:25:54,860
<font color="yellow">...tidak mengetahui situasi sebenarnya.</font>

343
00:25:56,360 --> 00:25:59,690
<font color="yellow">Dae Mok tidak lagi memiliki pil poppi.</font>

344
00:26:00,890 --> 00:26:03,420
<font color="yellow">Ladang poppi yang ia miliki telah terbakar habis.</font>

345
00:26:03,720 --> 00:26:04,890
<font color="yellow">Sekarang, dia...</font>

346
00:26:05,660 --> 00:26:09,290
<font color="yellow">...tidak bisa lagi mengontrol istana dengan pil poppi itu.</font>

347
00:26:09,490 --> 00:26:10,960
<font color="yellow">Apa itu benar?</font>

348
00:26:10,960 --> 00:26:13,220
<font color="yellow">Tidak bisa dipercaya.</font>

349
00:26:13,220 --> 00:26:15,960
<font color="yellow">Dia tidak memilikinya lagi? Sungguh?</font>

350
00:26:15,960 --> 00:26:18,720
<font color="yellow">Omong kosong macam apa lagi itu!?</font>

351
00:26:19,020 --> 00:26:21,060
<font color="yellow">Tidak benar bahwa ladang poppi telah terbakar habis!</font>

352
00:26:21,060 --> 00:26:23,720
<font color="yellow">- Kepala Kasim!
- Ya, Jeoha.</font>

353
00:26:23,720 --> 00:26:25,890
<font color="yellow">Daftar Kematian Pyunsoo-hwe, bawalah kemari.</font>

354
00:26:35,790 --> 00:26:36,890
<font color="yellow">Ini adalah...</font>

355
00:26:37,620 --> 00:26:39,690
<font color="yellow">Daftar Kematian yang dibuat Pyunsoo-hwe...</font>

356
00:26:39,690 --> 00:26:41,590
<font color="yellow">...setelah ladang poppi Pyunsoo-hwe terbakar habis.</font>

357
00:26:42,290 --> 00:26:43,390
<font color="yellow">Dae Mok...</font>

358
00:26:44,220 --> 00:26:46,020
<font color="yellow">...tidak peduli anggota Pyunsoo-hwe atau bukan,</font>

359
00:26:46,960 --> 00:26:49,120
<font color="yellow">siapa pun itu, bisa dibunuhnya.</font>

360
00:26:52,260 --> 00:26:54,660
<font color="yellow">Yeongsang Daegam. Daftar Kematian?</font>

361
00:26:54,660 --> 00:26:56,520
<font color="yellow">Apa yang dia katakan sekarang ini?</font>

362
00:26:57,060 --> 00:26:58,890
<font color="yellow">Dia berbohong untuk...</font>

363
00:26:58,990 --> 00:27:00,990
<font color="yellow">...menjatuhkan Pyunsoo-hwe!</font>

364
00:27:00,990 --> 00:27:02,060
<font color="yellow">Heo Yoo Geon.</font>

365
00:27:02,190 --> 00:27:05,290
<font color="yellow">Pada November 1693, kau adalah anggota pertama Pyunsoo-hwe.</font>

366
00:27:06,220 --> 00:27:09,520
<font color="yellow">I... Itu... bagaimana kau tahu?</font>

367
00:27:09,520 --> 00:27:12,890
<font color="yellow">Kau merencanakan segalanya dengan baik,
membantu Pyunsoo-hwe berkembang pesat,</font>

368
00:27:12,890 --> 00:27:13,990
<font color="yellow">namun...</font>

369
00:27:15,120 --> 00:27:18,420
<font color="yellow">...dosamu dengan mencoba menjadikan putrimu sebagai Ratu
dianggap sangat besar.</font>

370
00:27:18,660 --> 00:27:20,620
<font color="yellow">- Mati.
- Mati?</font>

371
00:27:22,420 --> 00:27:24,390
<font color="yellow">Maksudnya, kematianku?</font>

372
00:27:26,090 --> 00:27:30,090
<font color="yellow">Yeongsang Daegam, apa benar namaku terdapat dalam daftar itu?</font>

373
00:27:30,820 --> 00:27:32,220
<font color="yellow">Wakil Menteri!</font>

374
00:27:32,660 --> 00:27:36,090
<font color="yellow">Kau akan membiarkan dirimu dibodohi kebohongan semacam itu?</font>

375
00:27:39,890 --> 00:27:40,960
<font color="yellow">Ap--apa yang--</font>

376
00:27:42,260 --> 00:27:44,420
<font color="yellow">Ap--apa?</font>

377
00:27:44,420 --> 00:27:47,890
<font color="yellow">Kau yang mengelola ladang poppi,
jadi kau pasti tahu kebenarannya.</font>

378
00:27:48,560 --> 00:27:49,890
<font color="yellow">Katakan yang sebenarnya!</font>

379
00:27:50,190 --> 00:27:52,760
<font color="yellow">Sungguh ladang poppi telah terbakar habis?</font>

380
00:27:52,760 --> 00:27:53,890
<font color="yellow">Aku mengerti.</font>

381
00:27:54,220 --> 00:27:57,560
<font color="yellow">Aku akan mengatakan yang sebenarnya,
jadi tolong jangan mengamuk.</font>

382
00:27:59,760 --> 00:28:01,890
<font color="yellow">- Minggir!
- Tangkap dia!</font>

383
00:28:01,890 --> 00:28:04,360
<font color="yellow">- Tangkap dia!
- Astaga.</font>

384
00:28:04,360 --> 00:28:05,390
<font color="yellow">Minggir!</font>

385
00:28:05,390 --> 00:28:06,490
<font color="yellow">Oh... oh... astaga.</font>

386
00:28:07,220 --> 00:28:08,390
<font color="yellow">Je--Jeoha...</font>

387
00:28:09,320 --> 00:28:12,890
<font color="yellow">Sungguh... Dae Mok Eureushin...</font>

388
00:28:13,190 --> 00:28:16,860
<font color="yellow">...membuat Daftar Kematian tersebut?</font>

389
00:28:16,860 --> 00:28:19,360
<font color="yellow">Jumlah penawarnya sangat terbatas.</font>

390
00:28:19,360 --> 00:28:20,520
<font color="yellow">Total...</font>

391
00:28:21,020 --> 00:28:24,090
<font color="yellow">...ada 75 orang yang akan...</font>

392
00:28:25,420 --> 00:28:26,760
<font color="yellow">...menemui ajal mereka,</font>

393
00:28:27,720 --> 00:28:29,690
<font color="yellow">dalam lima hari ke depan.</font>

394
00:28:29,690 --> 00:28:31,290
<font color="yellow">Astaga. Astaga.</font>

395
00:28:31,290 --> 00:28:33,020
<font color="yellow">Lima hari? Apa?</font>

396
00:28:33,020 --> 00:28:34,520
<font color="yellow">Seja Jeoha.</font>

397
00:28:35,090 --> 00:28:37,720
<font color="yellow">Apakah nama saya juga ada dalam daftar itu?</font>

398
00:28:38,160 --> 00:28:39,690
<font color="yellow">Nama Busang juga ada.</font>

399
00:28:42,120 --> 00:28:43,390
<font color="yellow">Berengsek kau!</font>

400
00:28:43,460 --> 00:28:45,020
<font color="yellow">Kau bilang akan menyelamatkan kami,</font>

401
00:28:45,020 --> 00:28:47,260
<font color="yellow">rupanya kau coba membunuh kami semua!</font>

402
00:28:48,220 --> 00:28:49,320
<font color="yellow">Lepas!</font>

403
00:28:49,990 --> 00:28:51,560
<font color="yellow">Seja Jeoha.</font>

404
00:28:51,720 --> 00:28:53,960
<font color="yellow">Apakah nama saya juga ada dalam daftar?</font>

405
00:28:53,960 --> 00:28:55,460
<font color="yellow">Saya juga ada?</font>

406
00:28:55,460 --> 00:28:57,560
<font color="yellow">Jeoha, bagaimana dengan saya?</font>

407
00:28:57,560 --> 00:28:59,090
<font color="yellow">Apa saya ada dalam daftar?</font>

408
00:28:59,090 --> 00:29:00,290
<font color="yellow">Jeoha, tolong beritahu kami.</font>

409
00:29:00,290 --> 00:29:01,860
<font color="yellow">Semuanya!</font>

410
00:29:03,060 --> 00:29:04,960
<font color="yellow">Jangan bersikap kurang ajar!</font>

411
00:29:04,960 --> 00:29:07,890
<font color="yellow">Kalau ingin hidup, dengar aku baik-baik.</font>

412
00:29:09,220 --> 00:29:13,620
<font color="yellow">Aku, seperti kalian tahu, juga ketergantungan pada pil poppi.</font>

413
00:29:13,860 --> 00:29:16,220
<font color="yellow">Sekarang, untuk menyelamatkan nyawa kita semua,</font>

414
00:29:16,220 --> 00:29:18,090
<font color="yellow">hanya ada satu cara.</font>

415
00:29:19,990 --> 00:29:22,320
<font color="yellow">Dengan mengembalikan takhta pada Raja sesungguhnya.</font>

416
00:29:22,420 --> 00:29:24,520
<font color="yellow">Kita harus memercayai Kaisar kita...</font>

417
00:29:24,720 --> 00:29:27,620
<font color="yellow">...dan menyerahkan nyawa kita di tangannya.</font>

418
00:29:37,690 --> 00:29:41,360
<font color="yellow">Sekarang Seja adalah satu-satunya harapan kami.</font>

419
00:29:43,120 --> 00:29:45,290
<font color="yellow">Apa kau akan menyelamatkan kami?</font>

420
00:29:49,390 --> 00:29:50,760
<font color="yellow">Aku akan menyelamatkan semuanya.</font>

421
00:29:51,020 --> 00:29:53,560
<font color="yellow">Bagaimanapun caranya, aku akan mendapatkan penawarnya,</font>

422
00:29:53,960 --> 00:29:55,620
<font color="yellow">dan nyawa semua orang,</font>

423
00:29:56,890 --> 00:29:58,590
<font color="yellow">pasti kuselamatkan.</font>

424
00:30:01,260 --> 00:30:04,390
<font color="yellow">Kalian semua dengar kata-kata Seja?</font>

425
00:30:04,890 --> 00:30:06,460
<font color="yellow">Apakah kalian...</font>

426
00:30:06,720 --> 00:30:11,160
<font color="yellow">...bersama denganku, bersedia mengangkatnya kembali ke takhta Raja?</font>

427
00:30:11,220 --> 00:30:13,660
<font color="yellow">Ya, Daebi Mama.</font>

428
00:30:20,560 --> 00:30:21,990
<font color="yellow">Tunggu apa lagi?</font>

429
00:30:22,790 --> 00:30:25,190
<font color="yellow">Cepat bawa si palsu keluar dari sini!</font>

430
00:30:25,660 --> 00:30:26,820
<font color="yellow">Baik.</font>

431
00:30:32,490 --> 00:30:34,890
<font color="yellow">Jangan pikir membunuhku akan mengakhiri segalanya.</font>

432
00:30:35,020 --> 00:30:36,520
<font color="yellow">Jika penawarnya gagal didapat,</font>

433
00:30:36,520 --> 00:30:39,020
<font color="yellow">kalian semua juga akan mati!</font>

434
00:30:39,560 --> 00:30:42,090
<font color="yellow">Selain Dae Mok, tidak ada yang bisa membuat penawarnya.</font>

435
00:30:42,090 --> 00:30:44,960
<font color="yellow">Kalian semua hanya akan mati bersamaku!</font>

